{"id": "678183", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=678183", "title": "War of Information", "text": "Objectives.\nPlace &lt;a href=\"Eye%20of%20Hatred\"&gt;Eyes of Hatred&lt;/a&gt; in the House of Rituals in &lt;a href=\"Maldraxxus\"&gt;Maldraxxus&lt;/a&gt;, Eonian Archives in &lt;a href=\"Bastion\"&gt;Bastion&lt;/a&gt;, Tirna Vaal in &lt;a href=\"Ardenweald\"&gt;Ardenweald&lt;/a&gt;, and Castle Nathria in &lt;a href=\"Revendreth\"&gt;Revendreth&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nAh, the anointment oil. I had expected one of &lt;a href=\"Polemarch%20Adrestes\"&gt;Adrestes&lt;/a&gt;' recruits.\nNo matter. You seek my &lt;a href=\"memory\"&gt;memory&lt;/a&gt; for your trials, yes? I am afraid mere oil will not suffice.\nWith our house gone, we are left to fend for ourselves. Though this tower offers some protection, we are left cornered to any who may desire our end.\nInformation is the key to survival. Use my anointed talisman to give me eyes across all the realms...even in Bastion. Follow the list precisely--no questions.\nThen can we resolve payment.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nThere will be no negotiation in this matter.\nCompletion.\nAlready my vision grows. The pact is sealed."}
