it\"&gt;spit&lt;/a&gt; or throw rotten food such as an &lt;a href=\"https%3A//www.wowhead.com/spell%3D58511/rotten-apple-aroma\"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"https%3A//www.wowhead.com/spell%3D58514/rotten-banana-aroma\"&gt;Banana&lt;/a&gt;:"}
