{"id": "286884", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=286884", "title": "Warchief's Command Board", "text": "Warchief's Command Boards can be found at any major &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; hub in &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;. It offers level-appropriate quests for all zones. The quests offered are specific to their continent--that is, to see available &lt;a href=\"Kalimdor\"&gt;Kalimdor&lt;/a&gt; zones, one must visit the &lt;a href=\"Orgrimmar\"&gt;Orgrimmar&lt;/a&gt; board, and for &lt;a href=\"Eastern%20Kingdoms\"&gt;Eastern Kingdoms&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Undercity\"&gt;Undercity&lt;/a&gt; one. The equivalent billboard for the &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; is the &lt;a href=\"Hero%27s%20Call%20Board\"&gt;Hero's Call Board&lt;/a&gt;, an example of which can be found between the bank and the auction house in the &lt;a href=\"Trade%20District\"&gt;Trade District&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20City\"&gt;Stormwind City&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhile the quests posted on the board are not required and are merely &lt;a href=\"breadcrumb%20quest\"&gt;breadcrumb quest&lt;/a&gt;s, they are intended to help players who either do not know where to quest at their level or are simply ready for the next stage of their adventure."}
