{"id": "368537", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=368537", "title": "Warchief's fleet", "text": "The Warchief's fleet (or simply the orc fleet) consisted of three &lt;a href=\"Destroyer%23Orc%20destroyer\"&gt;destroyers&lt;/a&gt; sent from &lt;a href=\"Orgrimmar\"&gt;Orgrimmar&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=\"Garrosh\"&gt;Garrosh&lt;/a&gt; himself to aid in the &lt;a href=\"invasion%20of%20Gilneas\"&gt;invasion of Gilneas&lt;/a&gt;. They departed from &lt;a href=\"Bilgewater%20Harbor\"&gt;Bilgewater Harbor&lt;/a&gt;, a mistake that they would regret soon enough. When they left from the Harbor, the goblins gave them barrels of ale for the trip. Being see dogs, they drank it all and were drunk on their arrival. The worgen took the advantage and ambushed them on two of their ships, taking most of their lives and &lt;a href=\"Sea%20Dog%20Crate\"&gt;cargo&lt;/a&gt;. They crashed on the coast of &lt;a href=\"North%20Tide%27s%20Beachhead\"&gt;North Tide's Beachhead&lt;/a&gt;. The last ship landed at the shores of the &lt;a href=\"Skittering%20Dark\"&gt;Skittering Dark&lt;/a&gt;, those that didn't escape ended up as spider food. Those that survived are recovering at the &lt;a href=\"Forsaken%20Rear%20Guard\"&gt;Forsaken Rear Guard&lt;/a&gt;, still drunk from the experience. "}
