{"id": "685403", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=685403", "title": "Explore Torghast", "text": "Explore Torghast is the final quest of the Torghast quest chain in week one. In week two, (or twenty hours after turning in this quest), Bolvar will offer &lt;a href=\"Remnants%20of%20Hope\"&gt;Remnants of Hope&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Oribos\"&gt;Oribos&lt;/a&gt;.\nObjectives.\nExplore &lt;a href=\"Torghast%2C%20Tower%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;Torghast&lt;/a&gt; for clues to locate your allies.\nDescription.\n&lt;a href=\"Baine%20Bloodhoof\"&gt;Baine&lt;/a&gt; is safe, but our other allies are still prisoners of &lt;a href=\"the%20Jailer\"&gt;the Jailer&lt;/a&gt;. They remain in grave peril.\nTorghast is a constantly changing place, shifting according to the will of its master. It may be impossible to track them through normal means.\nEnter its cell blocks and see what information you can find. Seek any clue that might lead us to our missing friends, and bring it back to me.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nWhat did you find?\nCompletion.\n&lt;Bolvar studies the object intently.&gt;\nI sense a familiar essence. The holder of this key may have been involved in the capture of Jaina Proudmoore.\nI require time for further research. I will contact you once I determine our next course.\nNotes.\nBack into Torghast. This is a good time to turn in &lt;a href=\"Prison%20of%20the%20Forgotten\"&gt;Prison of the Forgotten&lt;/a&gt; and work on the &lt;a href=\"Runecarver\"&gt;Runecarver&lt;/a&gt;'s quest chain if desired.\nIn the main room, enter the wing marked on the minimap and progress through it. The marked wing will vary week by week, though it'll likely be &lt;a href=\"Skoldus%20Hall\"&gt;Skoldus Hall&lt;/a&gt; or the &lt;a href=\"Fracture%20Chambers\"&gt;Fracture Chambers&lt;/a&gt;, but all of the primary wings follow the same patterns of six floors: enemies (and floor bosses) on floors one, two, four, and five, a rest area on three, and the layer boss on six.\nThe wing boss will drop the &lt;a href=\"Soul-Touched%20Key\"&gt;Soul-Touched Key&lt;/a&gt;, which should get turned in to &lt;a href=\"Bolvar%20Fordragon\"&gt;Bolvar Fordragon&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Oribos\"&gt;Oribos&lt;/a&gt;.\nBolvar does not immediately offer a follow-up. Next week, (or 20 hours after turning this quest in in week 2 or beyond), Bolvar will push &lt;a href=\"Remnants%20of%20Hope\"&gt;Remnants of Hope&lt;/a&gt;, starting the next chapter.\nBeta version.\nExplore &lt;a href=\"Torghast%2C%20Tower%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;Torghast&lt;/a&gt; for clues to &lt;a href=\"Jaina%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Jaina&lt;/a&gt;'s location.\nYou have saved &lt;a href=\"Baine%20Bloodhoof\"&gt;Baine&lt;/a&gt; but our other friends are still missing. You'll need to find clues as to where they might be.\nTorghast is a constantly changing place, it may be impossible to track someone through normal means. For now, enter its cell blocks and see what information you can find regarding our missing numbers.\nHave you found anything?\nAn interesting find.\nThis creature you defeated may have been involved in the capture of Jaina.\nI will require some time to research this, I will contact you again once I have more information."}
{"id": "689225", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=689225", "title": "Explore Torghast Further", "text": "Objectives.\nExplore &lt;a href=\"Torghast%2C%20Tower%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;Torghast&lt;/a&gt; for clues to &lt;a href=\"Thrall\"&gt;Thrall's&lt;/a&gt; location.\nDescription.\nThere are still more to rescue from that place.\nSearch for more information about these Torment chambers, it seems like a likely place where others would be held.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nHave you found anything?\nCompletion.\nThis is not much to go on, but I shall have to make do for now.\nI will require some time to research this, I will contact you again once I have more information.\nNotes.\nBack into Torghast. As always, look at the map to see what wing the quest wants players to run. Keep an eye out for friendly NPCs that act like quest givers but aren't. For instance, a &lt;a href=\"Captive%20Dredger\"&gt;Captive Dredger&lt;/a&gt; has this gossip sequence:\nThis is enough to complete the quest. Finish the run or not, then head back to Oribos.\nBolvar will offer the followup quest in twenty hours."}
