{"id": "664629", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=664629", "title": "General Kaal", "text": "General Kaal is a &lt;a href=\"Stoneborn\"&gt;Stoneborn&lt;/a&gt; and commander of the &lt;a href=\"Stone%20Legion\"&gt;Stone Legion&lt;/a&gt; forces under &lt;a href=\"Sire%20Denathrius\"&gt;Sire Denathrius&lt;/a&gt;. Unlike other stoneborn, she is recognizable by her eyepatch and scarlet-gold armor. She serves alongside &lt;a href=\"General%20Grashaal\"&gt;General Grashaal&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Myskia\"&gt;Myskia&lt;/a&gt;. She is the final &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Sanguine%20Depths\"&gt;Sanguine Depths&lt;/a&gt;, where she escapes at 70%, and a dual-boss with Grashaal in &lt;a href=\"Castle%20Nathria\"&gt;Castle Nathria&lt;/a&gt; as the &lt;a href=\"Stone%20Legion%20Generals\"&gt;Stone Legion Generals&lt;/a&gt;.\nHistory.\nKaal served with &lt;a href=\"General%20Draven\"&gt;General Draven&lt;/a&gt; some time in the past, during which they were apparently close. She was once sent to the &lt;a href=\"Eternal%20Forge\"&gt;Eternal Forge&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Bastion\"&gt;Bastion&lt;/a&gt; on a secret mission to plant &lt;a href=\"anima\"&gt;anima&lt;/a&gt; siphons there.\nShe is first seen in the &lt;a href=\"Revendreth%20storyline\"&gt;Revendreth storyline&lt;/a&gt; meeting with the &lt;a href=\"Lord%20Chamberlain\"&gt;Lord Chamberlain&lt;/a&gt; and the Maw Walker to guide them to meeting the Master, &lt;a href=\"Sire%20Denathrius\"&gt;Sire Denathrius&lt;/a&gt;. She reassures Grashaal that the rebellion is finished, especially if Denathrius gets the Maw Walker to their side. \nOnce the Maw Walker eventually decides to join &lt;a href=\"Prince%20Renathal\"&gt;Prince Renathal&lt;/a&gt;'s rebellion, General Kaal fights the player during &lt;a href=\"The%20Master%20of%20Lies\"&gt;The Master of Lies&lt;/a&gt; along with General Grashaal and Myskia. &lt;a href=\"General%20Draven\"&gt;General Draven&lt;/a&gt; is able to goad the two Stone Legion Generals away from the player and the Prince as they advanced towards the Master. General Kaal is fought once again as the final boss of the &lt;a href=\"Sanguine%20Depths\"&gt;Sanguine Depths&lt;/a&gt;, attempting to stop the players from escaping with Denathrius' prized prisoner: &lt;a href=\"Z%27rali\"&gt;Z'rali&lt;/a&gt; the &lt;a href=\"Naaru\"&gt;Naaru&lt;/a&gt;. The heroes reduce her to 70% health before she overpowers them, forcing Draven to once again step in and give the heroes a chance to escape. Ultimately, Kaal is fought one final time as a &lt;a href=\"Stone%20Legion%20Generals\"&gt;dual-boss with Grashal&lt;/a&gt;, the penultimate boss in &lt;a href=\"Castle%20Nathria\"&gt;Castle Nathria&lt;/a&gt; where she finally meets her end.\nAdventure Journal.\n\"General Kaal stands as one of &lt;a href=\"Sire%20Denathrius\"&gt;Sire Denathrius&lt;/a&gt;'s main generals overseeing his operations in &lt;a href=\"Revendreth\"&gt;Revendreth&lt;/a&gt;. Strong, agile and full of guile, General Kaal uses her agility and &lt;a href=\"anima\"&gt;anima&lt;/a&gt;-infused nature to eliminate all who would stand against her master.\"\nOverview.\nGeneral Kaal is agile around the battlefield, working to weaken all of her opponents and removing them from the battlefield entirely."}
