{"id": "110386", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=110386", "title": "General Krakork", "text": "General Krakork is an &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"quest%20giver\"&gt;quest giver&lt;/a&gt; located in &lt;a href=\"Thrallmar\"&gt;Thrallmar&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Hellfire%20Peninsula\"&gt;Hellfire Peninsula&lt;/a&gt;. The hotheaded General commands Thrallmar's ground troops, answering directly to &lt;a href=\"Nazgrel\"&gt;Nazgrel&lt;/a&gt;. He is constantly on edge due to the extreme stresses of running a military operation against such an enemy as the &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Legion\"&gt;Burning Legion&lt;/a&gt; in such a setting as Hellfire Peninsula. \nQuotes.\nMake it quick, &lt;class&gt; - we've got a war to fight here, or hadn't you noticed?\nSpeculation.\nGeneral Krakork has the same skintone as the orcs of the &lt;a href=\"Blackrock%20clan\"&gt;Blackrock clan&lt;/a&gt;, implying that he may be a member of the clan."}
{"id": "620738", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=620738", "title": "General Krathax", "text": "General Krathax is a &lt;a href=\"sethrak\"&gt;sethrak&lt;/a&gt; who appears at or in the &lt;a href=\"Blistering%20Wastes\"&gt;Blistering Wastes&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Vol%27dun\"&gt;Vol'dun&lt;/a&gt; while the world quest &lt;a href=\"Azerite%20Mining%20%28Vol%27dun%29\"&gt;Azerite Mining (Vol'dun)&lt;/a&gt; is available. He is seen using a group of &lt;a href=\"Vulpera%20Slave\"&gt;Vulpera Slave&lt;/a&gt;s to mine a large &lt;a href=\"%3AAzerite\"&gt;:Azerite&lt;/a&gt; crystal, and he appears to be the leader of the &lt;a href=\"Faithless\"&gt;Faithless&lt;/a&gt;' Azerite mining operations in the area."}
