%27dal\"&gt;A'dal&lt;/a&gt; to protect and defend the city. It's likely that &lt;a href=\"Khadgar\"&gt;Khadgar&lt;/a&gt; asked A'dal to help the Lady.\nWhen the Horde attacked, he charged into the fray without hesitation, but was killed when &lt;a href=\"Garrosh%20Hellscream\"&gt;Garrosh Hellscream&lt;/a&gt; detonated a &lt;a href=\"mana%20bomb\"&gt;mana bomb&lt;/a&gt;, which destroyed the city. His body was later found by Jaina, and it may have been buried near Theramore with the rest of the fallen.\nQuotes.\nShould Kil'jaeden rise up through the Sunwell our world will be thrown into a war like the likes of which has not been seen for 10,000 years!"}
