{"id": "389932", "revid": "3154973", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=389932", "title": "Gerard (Tides of Darkness)", "text": "Gerard was a sailor and a friend of &lt;a href=\"Derek%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Derek Proudmoore&lt;/a&gt;. He was described as a veteran of many battles and served as a lookout on Derek's &lt;a href=\"Pride%20of%20Tiragarde\"&gt;ship&lt;/a&gt;. When the &lt;a href=\"Lost%20Fleet\"&gt;Third Fleet&lt;/a&gt; attacked the &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt;s, Gerard noticed &lt;a href=\"red%20dragon\"&gt;red dragon&lt;/a&gt;s and became very terrified but managed to tell it to Derek.\nIt is presumed that he died during the dragon attack."}
